{"tid":2142058,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"平食西餐好地方　$195歎理大酒管系學生誠意FYP","createTime":"2020-08-06T06:53:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T15:27:25.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d42241032df21b442ac8d6c0e3ee8e4d62ce94e7","tid":2142058,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peo6EFP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpeo6EFP.jpg&h=b6295959&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大學生的FYP（畢業作品）會做甚麼？論文？作品集？還是微電影？<br />\n<br />\n你有想過FYP可以經營餐廳嗎？由統籌到煮食都是出自學生手中，理工大學「酒店及旅遊業管理學系」的畢業作品就是要同學當一天餐廳經理。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，<br />\n想在一間幽靜、有氣氛的餐廳吃飯，<br />\n未計酒水加一，<br />\n閒閒地每人300元一餐，<br />\n但在尖東範圍竟有親民價的西餐存在。<br />\n<br />\n在理工大學<br />\n「酒店及旅遊業管理學系」學院底層，<br />\n向下走兩層，<br />\n再經過昏暗的長廊<br />\n就是Bistro 1979，<br />\n不是常客、不是旁邊Hotel ICON的住客，<br />\n都不會知道這餐廳的存在。"},{"pid":"9b74e1aefae8e357701b0a31864d3566ec7621b2","tid":2142058,"uid":166733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"考你有冇朋友嚟撐場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d00188d00e1edd4ec8c67f8a940df4569e194f","tid":2142058,"uid":231886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b74e1aefae8e357701b0a31864d3566ec7621b2","tid":2142058,"uid":166733,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T07:11:19.000Z","msg":"考你有冇朋友嚟撐場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T15:27:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2141510/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2141510/page/1</a><br />\n[整合] 中大湯宿傳銷狗<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">幫手推，要推到傳銷狗仆街</span></strong></span>"}]}